quran[7{c,v,t}:
60,12,"ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, jab tumahray paas momin aurtain baet karne ke liye ayen aur is baat ka ehad karen ke woh Allah ke sath kisi cheez ko shareek nah karen gi, chori nah karen gi, zina nah karen gi, apni aulaad ko qatal nah karen gi, apne haath paon ke agay koi bohtan ghurr kar nah layein gi, aur kisi amar Maroof mein tumhari nafarmani nah karen gi, to un se baet le lau aur unn ke haq mein Allah se duaye mughfirat karo, yaqeenan Allah dar guzar frmane wala aur reham karne wala hai"
60,13,"ae logo jo imaan laaye ho, unn logon ko dost nah banaao jin par Allah ne ghazab farmaya hai, jo akhirat se isi terhan mayoos hain jis terhan qabron mein parre hue kafir mayoos hain"
61,1,"Allah ki tasbeeh ki hai har uss cheez ne jo asmano aur zameen mein hai, aur woh ghalib aur hakeem hai"
61,2,"ae logo jo imaan laaye ho, tum kyun woh baat kehte ho jo karte nahi ho ?"
61,3,Allah ke nazdeek yeh sakht napasandeedah harkat hai ke tum kaho woh baat jo karte nahi
61,4,Allah ko to pasand woh log hain jo is ki raah mein is terhan saf basta ho kar lartay hain goya ke woh aik seesa pilayi hui deewar hain
61,5,"aur yaad karo moose ki woh baat jo is ne apni qoum se kahi thi"" ae meri qoum ke logo, tum kyun mujhe aziat dete ho halaank tum khoob jantay ho ke mein tumhari taraf Allah ka bheja howa rasool hon ?"" phir jab unhon ne theerh ikhtiyar ki to Allah ne un ke dil tirhhe kar diye, Allah فاسقوں ko hadaayat nahi deta"
